oll: the inner island would be one ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object, while the surrounding","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"}}}